- Total: ~440KB for typical 120×60 terrain

**Frame budget**:
- Snapshot generation: ~0.5ms (CPU)
- Mesh regeneration: ~2ms per chunk (CPU, only when dirty)
- GPU rendering: ~0.3ms (two draw calls)

